{
  "stem": "10818.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But they didn't want to keep me from being with my friends, and we were all together and looking out for each other.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But these were the little things that you expect children, you know, you expect to be able to do, to go swimming, and to go to the theater, and to the opera, and so on and so forth.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Sneaked into the theater and the opera a couple of times.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because well, as a child, people didn't know me, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I would go with a cousin or something.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I remember seeing, I think, and and so on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But that was very unofficial.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My parents couldn't go anymore.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They had their own, organized their own, what was called a kulturbund, which was a group of people.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They came-- came lectures, and singers, and concerts came in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And so they had that kind of entertainment, which was still first class in those days.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But so did I feel threatened?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] yes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was some unease.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was unease of, you know, if somebody wanted to haunt me, taunt me, they had the freedom to do it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And maybe once or twice, yes, there was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Never anybody I knew, but if they thought I was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And on Kristallnacht-- well, I don't know if you want me to talk about Kristallnacht.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Is this the appropriate time?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I'd like to just ask you before we get into Kristallnacht, if you look back and you think about that time, do you recall any opposition to the rise of Nazism within Mainz?",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I wasn't political.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, as Jews, we were opposed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we couldn't-- you know, I mean, there was nothing we could do.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
